{"tid":2433177,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大膽預測(繼續)","createTime":"2021-03-04T19:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T22:58:27.000Z","uid":38573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"889078889ccd6517699ffe88195c679bb0e97b04","tid":2433177,"uid":38573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T19:29:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2398857\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2398857</a><br />\n繼續9UP-2<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>美股呢兩個星期內應該會係上落市,磨一段時間,可能兩個星期,可能兩個月,<br />\n之後再有一個大回調,起碼2成<br />\n道指2萬9,我覺得係一個重要嘅指標<br />\n2萬4應該係底<br />\n<br />\n恆指睇法不變(恆指3月前會升到今年最高位之後就一直跌)<br />\n恆指可能會掂一掂3萬點,之後就可能會到返2萬點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n美股比我想像中早左回調<br />\n<br />\n納指:呢一波回調我估起碼仲有半個月時間,1萬2千應該係個關鍵位,跌穿就唔係叫回調,係真進入熊市,但本人唔係幾信會熊<br />\n短時間睇就跌得太多,要彈一彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n道指:我覺得係啱啱開始回調,重要指標2萬9,應該要1個月時間黎跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n恆指睇法不變,已經過左最高位,下次再升要等到年尾先有機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f99708564e4142d366150c9b25875eafefb7f1","tid":2433177,"uid":302314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T19:31:37.000Z","msg":"留多啲現金 等撈底<br />\n利申清咗7成倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859d5ab17676c57368fca28d640d44cdc16d1033","tid":2433177,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T19:40:52.000Z","msg":"又熊市 ？ 上年3月熊完 今舖又熊 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68dd1187b49a8c334517f09a5a4812b3d9c62239","tid":2433177,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T20:03:25.000Z","msg":"聽聞上年3月 HSI 都去唔到2萬點<br />\n我覺得期指到26800附近已經好唔錯"},{"pid":"0264ff7c6e13605ec9e07f0cb3ab025d1929dcd0","tid":2433177,"uid":38573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T19:33:06.00